pygtksourceview: pygtksourceview (Python Bindings for GtkSourceView)
pygtksourceview:
pygtksourceview: GtkSourceView is a text widget that extends the standard GTK+ 2.x
pygtksourceview: text widget GtkTextView. It improves GtkTextView by implementing
pygtksourceview: syntax highlighting and other features typical of a source editor.
pygtksourceview:
pygtksourceview: This package contains Python Bindings for GtkSourceView to allow
pygtksourceview: Python applications to take advantage of this widget.
